<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ش د ا:</span> <span class="c2">(الشَّادِي)</span> الْمُغَنِّي وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(شَدَا)</span> شِعْرًا أَوْ غِنَاءً إِذَا غَنَّى وَتَرَنَّمَ، وَبَابُهُ عَدَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>